1. Moj deda ima *farmu* pored reke. (My grandfather has a *farm* next to the river.)
2. Ovaj kraj je poznat po stočarstvu i *farmama*. (This area is known for livestock breeding and *farms*.)
3. Oni su nedavno kupili veliku *farmu* u okolini grada. (They recently bought a large *farm* in the outskirts of the city.)
4. Svinjsko meso koje jedemo nabavljamo sa *farme* koja se nalazi nedaleko odavde. (The pork we eat is sourced from a *farm* that's located nearby.)
5. *Farma* se bavi proizvodnjom organske hrane. (*Farm* is engaged in organic food production.)
6. Ona je zaposlena na jednoj od najvećih *farmerki* u državi. (She's employed at one of the largest *farms* in the country.)
7. Naša porodica već generacijama živi na *farmi*. (Our family has been living on a *farm* for generations.)
8. Država je odlučila da subvencioniše male *farmere*. (The government has decided to subsidize small *farmers*.)
9. Mnogi se odlučuju da kupuju organsku hranu jer znaju da dolazi sa *farmerki* koje ne koriste pesticide. (Many choose to buy organic food because they know it comes from *farms* that don't use pesticides.)
10. Njihov biznis se proširio sa jedne male *farme* na pet velikih *farmerki*. (Their business has expanded from one small *farm* to five large *farms*.)

(Note: "Farma" and "farmerka" are both Serbian words that refer to "farm" or "farmhouse," with "farmerka" specifically referring to a female farmer.)